[src:jmeter/component-reference-p01] Likewise, Headers are sent for the initial request, and won't be sent for the redirect.
[src:jmeter/component-reference-p01] This is generally only a problem for manually created test plans, as a test plan created using a recorder would continue from the redirected URL.
