[src:jmeter/component-reference-p01] If you are going to send multiple requests to the same LDAP server, consider using an LDAP Request Defaults Configuration Element so you do not have to enter the same information for each LDAP Request.
[src:jmeter/component-reference-p01] There are two ways to create test cases for testing an LDAP Server.
[src:jmeter/component-reference-p01] There are four test scenarios of testing LDAP.
[src:jmeter/component-reference-p01] User defined test: This will add the entry in the LDAP Server.
