[src:jmeter/component-reference-p02] It can be used to compare the value of a given attribute with some already known value.
[src:jmeter/component-reference-p02] In reality this is mostly used to check whether a given person is a member of some group.
[src:jmeter/component-reference-p02] In such a case you can compare the DN of the user as a given value, with the values in the attribute "member" of an object of the type groupOfNames.
